**Privacy Policy – Titanium Security**

### 1. Data Collected

The Bot may collect and process the following data:
• User IDs and Server (Guild) IDs
• Message content (only for moderation and security purposes)
• Moderation actions (warnings, bans, mutes, logs)
• Server configuration settings (automod rules, whitelist, etc.)

### 2. How Data is Used

Data is used strictly for:
• Detecting spam, malicious links, scams and unsafe content
• Preventing raids and abuse
• Executing moderation actions
• Maintaining server-specific configurations

### 3. Data Storage

• Data is stored securely and only as long as necessary
• Sensitive data is not shared with third parties
• No personal data is sold or used for advertising

### 4. Message Content

Message content is processed in real-time for moderation.
It is **not permanently stored**, except when required for logging moderation actions.

### 5. Data Sharing

No data is shared with third parties except:
• When required by law
• When necessary to protect security and integrity

### 6. User Rights

Users may request:
• Data removal
• Information about stored data

### 7. Security

Reasonable measures are taken to protect stored data from unauthorized access.

### 8. Changes

This policy may be updated at any time. Continued use of the Bot means acceptance of changes.
